# Flutter Feature Quick Start

Yeni feature oluşturmak için hızlı referans.

---

## 1. Klasör Yapısını Oluştur

```
feature/
└── [feature_name]/
    ├── data/
    │   ├── [feature]_remote_datasources.dart
    │   ├── [feature]_repository_impl.dart
    │   └── model/
    │       └── [feature]_model.dart
    ├── domain/
    │   ├── [feature]_repository.dart
    │   └── [feature]_usecases.dart
    └── presentation/
        ├── mixin/[feature]_mixin.dart
        ├── provider/[feature]_provider.dart
        └── view/[feature]_page.dart
```

---

## 2. Model

```dart
class FeatureModel {
  final String id;
  final String title;
  
  FeatureModel({required this.id, required this.title});
  
  factory FeatureModel.fromMap(Map<String, dynamic> map) =>
      FeatureModel(id: map['id'] ?? '', title: map['title'] ?? '');
}
```

---

## 3. Remote DataSource

```dart
class FeatureRemoteDataSource {
  final NetworkClient _client;
  FeatureRemoteDataSource(this._client);

  Future<List<FeatureModel>> getList() async {
    final res = await _client.get<Map<String, dynamic>>(ServicePath.featureList.value);
    final list = (res.data?['data'] as List?) ?? [];
    return list.map((e) => FeatureModel.fromMap(e)).toList();
  }
}
```

---

## 4. Domain Layer

```dart
// Abstract Repository
abstract class FeatureRepository {
  Future<Either<Failure, List<FeatureModel>>> getList();
}

// UseCases
class FeatureUseCases {
  final FeatureRepository _repo;
  FeatureUseCases(this._repo);
  
  Future<Either<Failure, List<FeatureModel>>> getList() => _repo.getList();
}
```

---

## 5. Repository Implementation

```dart
class FeatureRepositoryImpl extends BaseRepository implements FeatureRepository {
  final FeatureRemoteDataSource datasources;
  FeatureRepositoryImpl(this.datasources);

  @override
  Future<Either<Failure, List<FeatureModel>>> getList() =>
      guard(() => datasources.getList(), (data) => data);
}
```

---

## 6. Provider

```dart
class FeatureProvider extends ChangeNotifier {
  final FeatureUseCases uc;
  FeatureProvider(this.uc);

  Status status = Status.idle;
  List<FeatureModel> items = [];

  Future<void> getList() async {
    status = Status.loading;
    notifyListeners();

    final result = await uc.getList();
    result.fold(
      (fail) => status = Status.error,
      (data) {
        items = data;
        status = Status.success;
      },
    );
    notifyListeners();
  }
}
```

---

## 7. DI Kaydı (CustomLocator)

```dart
// product_state_container.dart içine ekle:
..registerFactory<FeatureRemoteDataSource>(
  () => FeatureRemoteDataSource(locator<NetworkClient>()),
)
..registerFactory<FeatureRepository>(
  () => FeatureRepositoryImpl(locator<FeatureRemoteDataSource>()),
)
..registerFactory<FeatureUseCases>(
  () => FeatureUseCases(locator<FeatureRepository>()),
)
..registerFactory<FeatureProvider>(
  () => FeatureProvider(locator<FeatureUseCases>()),
)
```

---

## 8. ProductStateItems

```dart
// product_state_items.dart içine ekle:
static FeatureProvider get featureProvider => CustomLocator.read<FeatureProvider>();
```

